'''Sardar Abdul Wahib''' (born 12 March 1901, date of death unknown) was an [[Afghanistan]] field hockey player, who competed at the [[1936 Summer Olympic Games]] and played in one game.<ref>[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/wa/sardar-abdul-wahib-1.html Sports-Reference Profile]</ref>

